.DT
change_goal_priority
Disk World creator help
change_goal_priority

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
change_goal_priority -  This method changes the priority of the specified goal.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void change_goal_priority(string goal)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^goal%^RESET%^ - the goal whose priority to change
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/npc/goals_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method changes the priority of the specified goal.  It will recall
the query_priority() method on the goal to figure out the new priority.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_goal_event(), remove_goal_event(), query_goal_priority()

.EP

